<lyrics>[V1]
 1- byk rby ạ̹ḥtmyt
 yạ mʿyny wmljạ̉y .. wṣkẖrẗ kẖlạṣy
 bkmạl qlbk rʿyt
 bmhạrẗ ạlạ̹ydyn .. ạ̹nt hdyt
 ạlqrạr- (mjdy wrạfʿ rạsy .. trsy wqrn kẖlạṣy
 nwry wḥṣn ḥyạty .. hạfḍl ạ̉gẖny lyk)2
 2- ʿyny sẖạyfẗ ạ̹ydyk
