 3- kẖyr kl ạlạ̉yạm
 wmrạḥm jwd wnʿmẗ .. ṭwl ḥyạty
 lmrạʿy kẖḍrạ tqwd
 lmyạh ạlrạḥẗ .. trsẖdny ạ̹ydyk</lyrics>
